    <body>
      <p id="ANOCQM0001">
      <pb n="[62]" />Anonymus</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0002">CAPITULUM DE QUATTUOR MENSURIS</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0003">Br1 8v</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0004">Item nota tria consistunt in cantu, scilicet modus [Lv on staff2], tempus [Bv on staff2], et prolatio [Sv on staff2].</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0005">Modus perfectus:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0006">[Lv,pt,Bv,Bv,Bv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0007">Tempus perfectum:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0008">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv,Sv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0009">Prolatio maior:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0010">[Sv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0011">Modus imperfectus:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0012">[Lv,pt,Bv,Bv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0013">Tempus imperfectum:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0014">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0015">Prolatio minor:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0016">[Sv,pt,Mv,Mv]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0017">Tempus et prolatio simul:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0018">
      <pb n="[63]" />Perfectum / maior:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0019">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv,Sv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv,pt on staff2]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0020">Perfectum / minor:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0021">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv,Sv,pt,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,pt on staff2]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0022">Imperfectum / maior:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0023">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,Mv,pt on staff2]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0024">Imperfectum / minor:</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0025">[Bv,pt,Sv,Sv,pt,Mv,Mv,pt,Mv,Mv,pt on staff2]</p>
      <p id="ANOCQM0026">In istis quattuor mensuris hic positis consistunt solum tempus et prolatio, et non modus, quia modus in quolibet istorum potest inveniri.</p>
